text: Rajdevi (Nepali: राजदेवी) is a municipality in Rautahat District, a part of Province No. 2 in Nepal. It was formed in 2016 occupying current 9 sections (wards) from previous 9 former VDCs. It occupies an area of 28.21 km2 with a total population of 31,212. ==References== Category:Populated places in Rautahat District Category:Nepal municipalities established in 2016
title: Rajdevi
